Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE is pleased to present the opportunity to acquire the fee simple interest in the iconic historic office building, the Salt Lake Stock Exchange. The Salt Lake Stock Exchange is located off Main Street, in the dynamic Salt Lake City, Central Business District. The property is surrounded by the vast retail, entertainment and recreational amenities found in downtown Salt Lake City. All three floors must be leased together.
